title: Logan Paul
description:
Logan Paul was at dinner when news of his sex tape broke. He went straight to Barstool HQ the next day to talk with KFC about whether or not it is him in the video. He also talks about his plans to continue boxing, why there is still bad blood with KSI, if he will fight in Rough N Rowdy, and challenges Antonio Brown to a fight.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
